values:
3 months; 
hours in the library, in front of the laptop; 
numerous backaches, headaches, wrist-aches; 
anxiety attacks, existential crises; 
$480 spent on laptop repair (it crashed! the horror!), 
at least $300 spent on zapping, printing, binding and comfort food.

MY HT FINAL DRAFT IS OUT!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

My baby stands proud at 75 pages, 13, 227 words!

Excuse me while I go and cry now.
